1 olive oil
1 cucumber
1 apple
1 packet roasted almonds
1 bag parsley
1 bag spinach & rocket mix
1 packet Grated Parmesan Cheese

• Thinly slice cucumber into half-moons. Thinly slice apple into wedges.

• Roughly chop roasted almonds and parsley.

• In a medium bowl, combine spinach & rocket mix, grated Parmesan
cheese, cucumber, apple, a pinch of salt and pepper and a drizzle of
olive oil.

• Transfer apple and Parmesan rocket salad to a serving dish. Drizzle with
some balsamic glaze.
• Sprinkle with almonds and parsley to serve. Enjoy!